description: So young and already in such a big trouble. When I visited the guy who called me last Monday I was surprised as I expected him to be older. And when he told me about his debts then he actually surprised me again. Almost 80 000 CZK. This is a small fortune. He moved into a new flat without paying any rent for over half a year. Additionally his former girlfriend abused his credit card. What can he do? Well, we do not grant any "loans" of above 40 000 or 50 000 CZK. This day I had only 30 thousand in my pocket. However, I still offered him my help. And as every crown should help this guy he agreed after a while. He was very shy but let me do anything with him that I wanted. He sucked me like a young god and didn´t even cry when I fucked him hard...
title: Debt Dandy 99
